abstract: RediClinic shut down its Wal-Mart walk-in clinics last year, but Wal-Mart has decided to go back into the clinic business with hospital affiliations.
snippet: RediClinic shut down its Wal-Mart walk-in clinics last year, but Wal-Mart has decided to go back into the clinic business with hospital affiliations.
lead_paragraph: Wal-Mart’s medical clinics are coming out of rehab.

headline.main: Wal-Mart Begins to Rebuild Health Clinic Business
